name: Bossk (V)
Lore: 'Male Trandoshan bounty hunter. Strong but clumsy. Extremely proud and arrogant. Suffered a humiliating defeat at the hands of Chewbacca and his partner Han Solo.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While at same site as a smuggler, power +3. While with opponent''s smuggler or Wookiee, opponent may not draw more than one battle destiny here. Immune to attrition < number of opponent''s smugglers on table.',
